             was indicted for that he <rs id="t17790707-48-off239" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17790707-48-off239" type="offenceCategory" value="breakingPeace"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17790707-48-off239" type="offenceSubcategory" value="libel"></interp>
               with a loud voice and in a publick open manner did sing, say, speak, utter, and pronounce divers false, scandalous, infamous, malicious, and obscene songs and and matters of and concerning 
                     <persName id="t17790707-48-victim511" type="victimName">
                        
                           <persName id="t17790707-48-victim512" type="victimName">
                              Elizabeth
                               the 
                              <rs id="t17790707-48-viclabel240" type="occupation">wife</rs>
                           <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17790707-48-victim512 t17790707-48-viclabel240"></join>
                           <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17790707-48-person513 t17790707-48-viclabel240"></join> of 
                                 <persName id="t17790707-48-person513" type="victimName">
                                    Joseph 
                                    Orpwood
                                 <interp inst="t17790707-48-person513" type="surname" value="Orpwood"></interp>
                              <interp inst="t17790707-48-person513" type="given" value="Joseph"></interp>
